edu.nd.darts.cimon
Interface CurrentNode<T>

All Known Implementing Classes:
CoordValNode, ValueNode
public interface CurrentNode<T>

Interface which defines nodes that maintain triple-linked-list structure for all actively monitored metrics. These nodes maintain the current value of the monitored metric, and a list of the periodic and condition monitoring requests.

Author:
darts
See Also:
ValueNode, CoordValNode

Insert new condition for specified threshold. If max is true, monitor as maximum threshold, otherwise monitor as minimum threshold.

Parameters:

insertOpportunistic

void insertOpportunistic(int monitorId,
                         long maxperiod,
                         Messenger callback,
                         long duration)
Insert opportunistic monitor (eavesdrop) to provide updated value whenever available, with maximum interval capped at _maxperiod_.

Parameters:
monitorId - unique id of monitor
maxperiod - maximum allowable period in milliseconds to provide updates
callback - messenger to handle callback with updated values
duration - duration to monitor, in milliseconds (0 for continuous)
